{"tid":576723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[得天下]「係咪鼓吹個個攞綜援」自力更生保安怒斥陳茂波","createTime":"2018-03-01T06:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T16:49:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e313ac0b29cbcfaf66a680b3a6193fdbff78b6c","tid":576723,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】新一份《財政預算案》昨日正式出爐，庫房水浸但未必人人受惠，其中一項綜援出「三糧」，更惹起不滿。今早財政司長陳茂波出席電台聯播節目，從事保安的聽眾致電，怒斥「咁多年努力唔想攞綜援，係咪鼓吹香港人個個攞綜援？」<br />\n<br />\n張先生表示自己從事保安業，接近60歲，女兒今年完成中六，經已無法受惠DSE免考試費，自己多年來努力不拿攞綜援，但現時綜援出「三糧」，他反問「係咪鼓吹香港人個個攞綜援」。他又指不是認為低收入人士不值幫忙，但「你畀1個月咪得囉，你畀2個月做乜」，又言即使不派6000元，全民派500元也好。<br />\n<br />\n由於節目時間關係，陳茂波簡單回應指，對低收入家庭有提出措施幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E5%80%8B%E5%80%8B%E6%94%9E%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%80%92%E6%96%A5%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-010600051.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%2590%25B9%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2594%259E%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%2596%25A5%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2-010600051.html&d=8rO1rbVA40XkarO3f2SivKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fa90bdc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E5%80%8B%E5%80%8B%E6%94%9E%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%80%92%E6%96%A5%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-010600051.html</a>"},{"pid":"6bbb6eeda849d3956409a4eae6c4f4cdfce95bd6","tid":576723,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Answer is <span style=\"color: